paragraphs.title: Pick a Point-of-Interest (POI)
paragraphs.text:
%spark

import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.{regexp_extract}
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.{RegexTokenizer, Tokenizer}

val id = z.input("Enter POI (IP Address):")

// Extract POI Device
val t0 = java.lang.System.currentTimeMillis()
val POIDevice = queryToDS(connection, "select * from device_info where ip = '" + id + "'").collect()


val deviceDS = queryToDS(connection, "select * from device_topology where topology like '%"+id+"%'")
val devicetopology = deviceDS.collect


// Extract Parent Devices
val t1 = java.lang.System.currentTimeMillis()
val pattern_parent = id.toString + ".+"
val parent_regexTokenizer = new RegexTokenizer().setInputCol("TOPOLOGY").setOutputCol("parents").setPattern(pattern_parent).setGaps(false)
val parent_regexTokenized = parent_regexTokenizer.transform(deviceDS)
    .select("parents").withColumn("parents2", regexp_replace($"parents"(0), id.toString+"\\|", ""))
    .drop("parents")
val parentDevices     = parent_regexTokenized.select("parents2").rdd.map(r => r(0).toString.split("\\|")).flatMap(x => x).distinct().collect
val parentDevicesStr  = parentDevices.mkString("|")
val parentDevicesInfo = queryToDS(connection, "select * from device_info where ip in ("+ parentDevices.map(x => "'"+x+"'").mkString(",") +")" ).collect

val parent_runtime = (java.lang.System.currentTimeMillis() - t1).toString


// Extract Children Devices
val t2 = java.lang.System.currentTimeMillis()
val pattern_children = ".*?" + id.toString
val children_regexTokenizer = new RegexTokenizer().setInputCol("TOPOLOGY").setOutputCol("children").setPattern(pattern_children).setGaps(false)
val children_regexTokenized = children_regexTokenizer.transform(deviceDS)
    .select("children").withColumn("children2", regexp_replace($"children"(0), id.toString+"\\|", ""))
    .drop("children")
val childrenDevices     = children_regexTokenized.select("children2").rdd.map(r => r(0).toString.split("\\|")).flatMap(x => x).distinct().collect
val childrenDevicesStr  = childrenDevices.mkString("|")
val childrenDevicesInfo = queryToDS(connection, "select * from device_info where ip in ("+ childrenDevices.map(x => "'"+x+"'").mkString(",") +")" ).collect


println("\r\n\r\n")
println("Got " + parentDevicesInfo.size.toString + " parent devices in " + parent_runtime + " ms")
println("Got " + childrenDevicesInfo.size.toString + " child devices in " + (java.lang.System.currentTimeMillis() - t2).toString + " ms")
println("\r\n\r\n")


z.angularBind("poidevice", POIDevice)
z.angularBind("parents", parentDevicesInfo)
z.angularBind("parentsStr", parentDevicesStr)
z.angularBind("children", childrenDevicesInfo)
z.angularBind("childrenStr", childrenDevicesStr)
z.angularBind("devicetopology", devicetopology)
z.angularBind("id", id)
z.run("20161112-195716_1056217064")


childrenDevicesInfo.foreach(x => println(x))
